1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 5]

5
00:01:15,110 --> 00:01:16,450
It's not that I don't want to help you.

6
00:01:17,390 --> 00:01:18,980
But a cultivation vessel is something you're born with.

7
00:01:19,830 --> 00:01:20,650
There's no artifact

8
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:23,370
that can make one.

9
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:28,700
But I've heard

10
00:01:29,190 --> 00:01:31,170
the academy's herb garden is second to none.

11
00:01:31,750 --> 00:01:33,220
Maybe they've got

12
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,980
some rare treasure that can reshape your meridians.

13
00:01:36,670 --> 00:01:37,860
You're right.

14
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:40,730
- I'll go find it... - Hold on.

15
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,010
I heard

16
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:49,250
Elder Zhu, who runs the garden, is strict and fair.

17
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,140
He won't just

18
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,370
give it to you.

19
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:53,810
Unless

20
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,580
you're someone he really values.

21
00:01:59,670 --> 00:02:00,420
Like him.

22
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:04,450
A top-tier Metal Spirit Root.

23
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,850
There's stagnant energy around your heart meridians.

24
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,530
Have you been injured lately?

25
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:27,500
Injured?

26
00:02:33,550 --> 00:02:34,530
Could it be

27
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,900
Hu Jiaping's doing back then?

28
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,810
Good thing you came in time.

29
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:40,370
Or that stagnant energy would've damaged your heart meridians.

30
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:43,300
No worries. I'll clear it with some acupuncture.

31
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,780
Could you step out for a bit?

32
00:02:47,390 --> 00:02:47,940
Mr. Zhu,

33
00:02:48,670 --> 00:02:50,370
do you have any elixir

34
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,130
that can heal internal injuries,

35
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,130
boost cultivation,

36
00:02:53,430 --> 00:02:54,570
and fix a cultivation vessel?

37
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,850
What are you up to?

38
00:02:59,590 --> 00:03:01,690
Give this top-tier Metal Spirit Root a little boost.

39
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,740
Look.

40
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,780
Go check... that cabinet...

41
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,780
- over there. - Okay.

42
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,850
This looks like a treasure.

43
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,410
It...

44
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,570
My Divine Tree 1000!

45
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,340
Look what you've done!

46
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:15,810
I just touched it.

47
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:16,660
Really.

48
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:17,420
It...

49
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:20,420
Is it really rare?

50
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:21,300
Want me

51
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:23,100
to find you a new one?

52
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,690
Can't find another.

53
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:28,810
The Divine Tree is the most mystical tree in the world.

54
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,300
Born from chaos,

55
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:32,570
it gathers all living vitality.

56
00:04:32,910 --> 00:04:34,890
It bears a single fruit every five hundred years.

57
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,130
I failed again.

58
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,690
I got scammed

59
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:44,250
999 times

60
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:48,940
before I got this Divine Tree 1000!

61
00:04:51,030 --> 00:04:52,180
This one's fake too.

62
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,740
Shanhua once told me

63
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,180
the Divine Tree is an immortal, nature-born tree.

64
00:04:59,910 --> 00:05:01,130
Even if struck by heavenly lightning,

65
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,100
it will revive.

66
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:04,300
It never rots.

67
00:05:11,150 --> 00:05:12,100
I got scammed again.

68
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,690
Is the Divine Tree so powerful?

69
00:05:15,030 --> 00:05:15,890
What's its story?

70
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:18,250
Five hundred years ago, when the Sea Calamity struck,

71
00:05:18,910 --> 00:05:21,100
the Yecha demon clan appeared with the Divine Tree,

72
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,570
trying to overthrow the Central Plains.

73
00:05:22,790 --> 00:05:25,620
Fortunately, a master from Wuyue Court defeated the Demon Lord

74
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,300
and saved the world from ruin.

75
00:05:28,350 --> 00:05:30,740
That master sounds incredible.

76
00:05:31,590 --> 00:05:32,860
He also created many cultivation techniques.

77
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,330
Each one with power beyond imagination.

78
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:08,250
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

79
00:06:08,570 --> 00:06:11,050
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

80
00:06:11,530 --> 00:06:14,850
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

81
00:06:15,090 --> 00:06:16,080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

82
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:16,810
What's happening to me?

83
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:19,660
Whose memories are these?

84
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,810
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

85
00:06:22,530 --> 00:06:24,890
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

86
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:27,400
♪No calamity can rival♪

87
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,840
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

88
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:36,420
This is your reward for helping me find the medicine.

89
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:37,420
Now we're even.

90
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,250
Relax.

91
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,770
This pill stabilizes your core and heals injuries.

92
00:06:49,790 --> 00:06:50,570
It won't poison you.

93
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,180
But

94
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,330
after this, we go our separate ways.

95
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,130
Stay away from me.

96
00:07:41,910 --> 00:07:42,540
What's wrong with you?

97
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:47,660
Your Highness?

98
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:53,180
Did Elder Zhu mess up the needles?

99
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,810
He can barely stand.

100
00:07:56,470 --> 00:07:58,420
I'll go back to take some medicine and recover.

101
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,570
I'll leave Xiuyuan to you.

102
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:09,770
It's been four hours.

103
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,810
They could've at least sent word.

104
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,740
Alright. We'll stop waiting.

105
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,450
Let's go.

106
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,010
Your Ladyship.

107
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:17,940
Your Ladyship.

108
00:08:22,790 --> 00:08:23,210
Your Ladyship!

109
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,300
- Who? - Lanya.

110
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,140
It's a formation!

111
00:08:35,710 --> 00:08:38,020
This batch of disciples is so clueless.

112
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:40,420
It took them this long to realize they were trapped.

113
00:08:41,230 --> 00:08:42,420
In a real fight,

114
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:44,780
they'd be dead a hundred times over.

115
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,330
Ms. Lin is so harsh.

116
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,730
A formation is about alignment.

117
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,300
It maps the cosmic and earthly veins

118
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:11,060
through numerical variations.

119
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:14,690
By channeling spirit energy, it strikes unseen.

120
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:30,660
Focus on guiding your spirit energy,

121
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:32,300
and you'll see the way out.

122
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:38,380
Hurry.

123
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:38,940
I'll wait for you.

124
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,730
Wait... for me?

125
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:41,730
Why?

126
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:43,330
To watch me fail? Just go.

127
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:12,420
Xiaobangchui, drawing talismans is actually simple.

128
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:15,420
Let your hand follow

129
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,140
what your mind sees.

130
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:57,210
She actually altered the formation.

131
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:11,570
Is she connected to the master who set the formation in Gaolu?

132
00:11:39,070 --> 00:11:43,430
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

133
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:45,840
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

134
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:51,550
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

135
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:55,720
♪Climb high, lone sword sings, dance beneath autumn moon♪

136
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:57,970
Lifei, you did it!

137
00:11:58,280 --> 00:12:03,840
♪Rough the road, yet my steps shall never cease to move♪

138
00:12:04,110 --> 00:12:06,110
♪Banners wave, war drums thunder across the sky♪

139
00:12:06,110 --> 00:12:07,490
Using runes to channel spirit power.

140
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:09,210
Very clever.

141
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:10,940
Not at all.

142
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,540
It's just cheap tricks.

143
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:15,970
Tongzhou, why praise her and not me?

144
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:20,120
♪Let frost, snow and rain block the long stone steps♪

145
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:22,440
♪I tread fleeting mist beneath my feet♪

146
00:12:24,990 --> 00:12:25,660
Great.

147
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:28,300
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

148
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:38,040
♪Don't idle away time. We shall meet atop the peak♪

149
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,260
Can't catch a break, can we?

150
00:12:53,710 --> 00:12:54,380
Bees?

151
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:22,180
Help!

152
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:28,380
Xiuyuan!

153
00:13:28,590 --> 00:13:29,140
Hold on to me.

154
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:41,310
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

155
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:42,750
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

156
00:13:42,750 --> 00:13:44,060
Are these bees crazy?

157
00:13:44,590 --> 00:13:45,830
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

158
00:13:45,830 --> 00:13:46,570
Could it be...?

159
00:13:46,870 --> 00:13:47,450
It wasn't me!

160
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:50,350
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

161
00:13:51,390 --> 00:13:54,870
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

162
00:13:55,590 --> 00:13:57,950
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

163
00:13:58,550 --> 00:14:00,070
♪No calamity can rival♪

164
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:03,510
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

165
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,660
Where are we?

166
00:14:23,470 --> 00:14:24,900
This is the kitchen of Qiaoshan Hall.

167
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,420
So I made it to the cafeteria.

168
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,690
Too bad.

169
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,570
Missed mealtime.

170
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:37,850
If you're hungry,

171
00:14:38,680 --> 00:14:39,490
I'll go find you something to eat.

172
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:46,780
Here.

173
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:00,300
Um,

174
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:01,850
you don't have to be so nice to me.

175
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:06,260
I should repay you for saving my life.

176
00:15:08,470 --> 00:15:09,570
You don't have to.

177
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:11,090
I didn't even mean to save you.

178
00:15:43,990 --> 00:15:44,690
There's a restriction spell.

179
00:15:45,470 --> 00:15:46,420
Who's playing tricks here?

180
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:51,260
By the power of the spirits,

181
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:53,610
break!

182
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:22,020
By the power of the spirits, break!

183
00:17:32,230 --> 00:17:32,900
What's wrong with you?

184
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:37,660
Are you okay?

185
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:42,490
What's happening?

186
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:46,450
What are you doing?

187
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:52,340
Have you lost your mind?

188
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:19,450
Are you alright?

189
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:29,770
Talk.

190
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:31,250
Who sent you?

191
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:32,250
Why are you trying to kill us?

192
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,420
Staying silent, huh?

193
00:18:39,360 --> 00:18:40,050
Keep it up,

194
00:18:40,790 --> 00:18:42,100
and I'll toss you into a hotpot.

195
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:50,450
Mr. Hu,

196
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:51,690
this coriander spirit...

197
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,340
That's no coriander spirit.

198
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:58,420
This is my pet, Xiangxiang.

199
00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:00,210
Xiangxiang...?

200
00:19:00,230 --> 00:19:01,730
I was wondering where it went.

201
00:19:02,230 --> 00:19:03,530
So you two caught it.

202
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,340
What?

203
00:19:05,990 --> 00:19:07,140
The grilled fish wasn't enough,

204
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,620
and you wanted a side dish?

205
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:09,900
No.

206
00:19:10,510 --> 00:19:11,250
It just suddenly...

207
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:13,180
It was suddenly interrupted during its cultivation.

208
00:19:13,710 --> 00:19:14,690
Since it's your first offense,

209
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:15,580
I'll let it slide.

210
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:21,380
Mr. Hu, we're just letting it go?

211
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:22,730
What else?

212
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,770
You two broke into the kitchen.

213
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:27,340
Still here? Waiting to be punished?

214
00:19:32,470 --> 00:19:33,050
Get going.

215
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:38,450
Xiangxiang,

216
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:40,450
you naughty thing.

217
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:41,770
Good thing I got here in time.

218
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,420
One more step late

219
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,620
and you'd have been...

220
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,530
I told you to place a seal on them.

221
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:50,970
Look at you,

222
00:19:51,230 --> 00:19:52,420
getting captured instead.

223
00:19:53,360 --> 00:19:55,730
I did cast the spell just as you told me.

224
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:58,530
But suddenly I smelled

225
00:19:58,550 --> 00:19:59,730
something so tempting.

226
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:02,210
And I don't remember anything after that.

227
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,140
By the time I was caught,

228
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:06,100
demonic energy had already invaded my body.

229
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:08,970
Mr. Hu, Lei Xiuyuan

230
00:20:08,990 --> 00:20:10,770
is so scary.

231
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,860
Demonic energy?

232
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,620
Looks like our plan backfired.

233
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:22,620
Our good days are coming to an end.

234
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:26,450
We need to eliminate them first.

235
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,690
Coincidences don't just happen.

236
00:20:32,230 --> 00:20:34,450
Someone must be behind that bee incident.

237
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,290
Hu Jiaping showed up at the exact perfect moment.

238
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:39,210
Definitely suspicious.

239
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:50,940
Why did you pull me just now?

240
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,340
You're acting weird.

241
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:01,580
What are you thinking?

242
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,970
I knew something was off with you.

243
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:27,050
Did he notice

244
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:29,250
Riyan hidden in my hair?

245
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:31,050
Probably not.

246
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,620
You're pretty good-looking.

247
00:21:49,470 --> 00:21:51,100
But why are you always trying to bite people?

248
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,050
What's wrong with you?

249
00:21:53,470 --> 00:21:55,730
Fine. I'm magnanimous.

250
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:56,620
I won't hold it against you.

251
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:07,820
Quiet down, everyone!

252
00:22:08,710 --> 00:22:11,210
Chufeng Academy has been around for a hundred years.

253
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,660
It's where

254
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,690
elite disciples are chosen for the great sects.

255
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:17,660
It's no place for those who don't measure up.

256
00:22:18,230 --> 00:22:19,770
Those with poor aptitude

257
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,970
or those who slipped in by luck

258
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:25,860
will be exposed in the monthly exam.

259
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:29,580
Mr. Hu,

260
00:22:30,230 --> 00:22:31,010
am I right?

261
00:22:36,710 --> 00:22:37,970
Absolutely right.

262
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,620
If that's the case,

263
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:41,860
then some people who don't belong here

264
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:43,690
will definitely be leaving.

265
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:49,490
Never heard anyone admit that about themselves.

266
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:57,530
Youran,

267
00:22:58,200 --> 00:23:00,050
is the monthly exam every month?

268
00:23:00,230 --> 00:23:01,140
Of course not.

269
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:02,660
That'd be such a hassle.

270
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:05,420
This one was Mr. Hu's idea.

271
00:23:06,990 --> 00:23:08,450
Ten days left until the monthly exam.

272
00:23:09,270 --> 00:23:11,290
Hope you'll all work hard

273
00:23:11,990 --> 00:23:13,420
and not disappoint the masters.

274
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,180
Mr. Hu,

275
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:18,820
what happens if someone fails the monthly exam?

276
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:21,450
If you fail,

277
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:23,380
of course you have to

278
00:23:23,790 --> 00:23:25,210
leave the academy.

279
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:50,660
I don't know if it was that coriander spirit,

280
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:53,100
but last night I felt dizzy and restless. Couldn't control myself.

281
00:23:55,270 --> 00:23:55,820
Sorry.

282
00:23:56,790 --> 00:23:57,420
Forget it.

283
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:00,820
Anyway, I know why you approached me now.

284
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:03,340
It's for Riyan, isn't it?

285
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:06,820
Someone's using Shanhua's life to force you?

286
00:24:09,600 --> 00:24:10,860
He was Shanhua's master.

287
00:24:12,230 --> 00:24:12,970
But I never expected...

288
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:14,730
I caused Shanhua's suffering.

289
00:24:19,030 --> 00:24:20,450
I feel sorry for you,

290
00:24:20,470 --> 00:24:21,100
but

291
00:24:22,030 --> 00:24:22,940
I won't help you.

292
00:24:23,840 --> 00:24:24,770
Everyone's busy.

293
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:26,180
We handle our own problems.

294
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,210
I know.

295
00:24:28,230 --> 00:24:29,180
We have to rely on ourselves.

296
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:30,940
My cultivation is still weak.

297
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:33,490
Only by staying here and learning techniques

298
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,050
can I save Shanhua.

299
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:38,180
It's good that you figured that out.

300
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,490
But now, with powerful enemies around,

301
00:24:42,030 --> 00:24:43,140
if we want to stay,

302
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,450
we need to work together.

303
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,290
Work together?

304
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:47,690
How?

305
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:08,380
Whenever I went on a mission with my master,

306
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,690
we'd always track and scout first

307
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:10,860
to know our enemy.

308
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:12,450
You mean swindling people?

309
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:15,050
It's called thorough planning and problem-solving.

310
00:25:26,270 --> 00:25:27,860
This is Ms. Mu's place?

311
00:25:33,470 --> 00:25:34,140
You know,

312
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:36,210
whether it's a hero or a fool,

313
00:25:36,230 --> 00:25:37,580
they all fall for a pretty face.

314
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:38,660
Focus on the mission.

315
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:42,530
Mu.

316
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:44,210
Mu!

317
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:45,580
Mu!

318
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:46,820
Let me go!

319
00:25:47,070 --> 00:25:48,050
Don't come to me again!

320
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,250
Catch him red-handed.

321
00:25:55,030 --> 00:25:55,940
Go inform the headmaster.

322
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,580
When you see him, just say

323
00:25:58,840 --> 00:26:01,100
Hu Jiaping tried to force himself on Mu after being rejected.

324
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:02,420
He's vile. This is an emergency.

325
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,010
Hurry!

326
00:26:42,120 --> 00:26:43,250
You creep!

327
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:57,940
You again?

328
00:26:58,710 --> 00:26:59,900
Die!

329
00:27:31,120 --> 00:27:31,820
By the power of the spirits,

330
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:32,380
break!

331
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:37,380
Cheap tricks.

332
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:38,730
Which old scumbag taught you that?

333
00:27:39,470 --> 00:27:40,530
Old scumbag?

334
00:27:41,470 --> 00:27:42,450
You're the old scumbag!

335
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:43,250
I'll slam you down!

336
00:27:43,550 --> 00:27:44,770
I'll throw you down!

337
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:45,530
I'll slam...

338
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:46,250
I...

339
00:27:46,360 --> 00:27:46,970
Lifei.

340
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,010
Lifei.

341
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:52,290
Ms. Mu,

342
00:27:52,550 --> 00:27:53,180
don't be afraid.

343
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:53,940
The headmaster is on his way.

344
00:27:54,070 --> 00:27:55,530
This monster won't get his way.

345
00:27:58,230 --> 00:27:58,900
Put her down now!

346
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:10,490
Mu!

347
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:12,530
Mu.

348
00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:14,490
Are you okay, Mu?

349
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:15,140
Mu!

350
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:16,420
Are you alright, Mu?

351
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,450
Are you hurt?

352
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:18,770
Easy.

353
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:20,490
Here.

354
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,450
You're still doing that?

355
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,210
Stop!

356
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:28,580
Mr. Zuo.

357
00:28:30,510 --> 00:28:31,050
Lifei,

358
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,620
you've all misunderstood.

359
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,900
Jiaping was just healing Mu's injuries.

360
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,010
Mr. Zuo.

361
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,290
How are you?

362
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:45,860
I'm fine.

363
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:47,900
Sorry to make you worry.

364
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,730
You two, come with me.

365
00:29:07,600 --> 00:29:11,140
Mu was originally a sword called Lifeng,

366
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:13,250
of Immortal Guangwei of Wuyue Court.

367
00:29:13,710 --> 00:29:17,050
She and Jiaping grew up together.

368
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,730
They were deeply in love.

369
00:29:19,710 --> 00:29:20,450
Sadly,

370
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:22,530
when they went to Kongsang to fight monsters,

371
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:24,660
Mu's blade broke, and her primordial spirit

372
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:27,730
was severely damaged while saving Jiaping.

373
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:32,420
Guangwei sent Mu to the academy to recover.

374
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:34,660
But

375
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,530
Jiaping defied

376
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:39,210
his master's orders for Mu,

377
00:29:39,840 --> 00:29:41,580
abandoned the righteous path of cultivation,

378
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,860
and left Wuyue Court.

379
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:45,490
That madman...

380
00:29:48,550 --> 00:29:50,450
Mr. Hu is quite the romantic.

381
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:55,290
For all these years,

382
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:59,530
he's been searching for a way to reforge Lifeng,

383
00:30:00,990 --> 00:30:02,210
but never found one.

384
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:05,620
Since humans and spirits are different,

385
00:30:05,790 --> 00:30:07,180
Mu refused to drag Jiaping down.

386
00:30:07,470 --> 00:30:08,770
She's been avoiding him.

387
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:14,530
That's why you saw what happened earlier.

388
00:30:17,510 --> 00:30:18,660
If you ask me,

389
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,450
the academy's rules need to change.

390
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:25,180
How so?

391
00:30:26,710 --> 00:30:28,820
On our first day here, you said

392
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,140
cultivation

393
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,770
means letting go of worldly ties.

394
00:30:32,030 --> 00:30:33,140
My master also said

395
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:36,010
cultivation is about transcending worldly conventions.

396
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:38,770
These two are clearly in love.

397
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,140
They end up like a miserable couple.

398
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:41,100
What does that show?

399
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:45,140
It shows our academy has failed in its teaching.

400
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:50,020
Are your sunflower seeds tasty?

401
00:30:52,270 --> 00:30:54,090
It shows Mr. Hu

402
00:30:54,350 --> 00:30:55,850
is narrow-minded

403
00:30:55,870 --> 00:30:56,690
and cowardly.

404
00:30:57,270 --> 00:30:59,180
He can't let go of gossip or prejudice.

405
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,770
How can he even cultivate like this?

406
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:01,770
So rigid.

407
00:31:02,070 --> 00:31:03,180
How can he teach disciples?

408
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:05,690
If you ask me, he should be

409
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:07,290
expelled.

410
00:31:07,710 --> 00:31:08,530
Let him reflect on himself.

411
00:31:13,790 --> 00:31:15,490
If Hu Jiaping gets kicked out,

412
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,580
everyone will be thrilled.

413
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:19,420
You don't hold prejudice against other races.

414
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,140
That's good.

415
00:31:21,990 --> 00:31:22,940
But in this world,

416
00:31:23,230 --> 00:31:25,970
it's hard for different races to accept each other.

417
00:31:26,510 --> 00:31:29,660
Public opinion can destroy a person.

418
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,420
If public opinion can break you,

419
00:31:39,230 --> 00:31:41,250
it just means your will isn't strong enough.

420
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,580
If it were me,

421
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:46,010
I wouldn't care if he's human or a demon.

422
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:47,580
If we truly loved each other,

423
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:48,900
I'd tear down every obstacle

424
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:50,010
and never back down.

425
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:55,290
Lifei,

426
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:58,010
you haven't yet experienced the world's suffering.

427
00:31:58,550 --> 00:32:00,140
You can't understand others' pain.

428
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:04,140
The mortals have their laws and conventions.

429
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:09,010
And we immortals have our rules and order.

430
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,420
It's a long story.

431
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:13,340
You'll understand

432
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,530
in time.

433
00:32:19,510 --> 00:32:20,620
It's getting late.

434
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:23,620
I should rest.

435
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:31,340
Mr. Zuo.

436
00:32:34,470 --> 00:32:35,380
Do you also think

437
00:32:36,030 --> 00:32:36,820
it's not worth

438
00:32:37,710 --> 00:32:39,010
doing things you shouldn't

439
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:40,420
for personal feelings?

440
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:45,010
Whether it's worth it

441
00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:46,860
comes down to your own heart.

442
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:49,290
Every encounter

443
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:51,340
has its own karma.

444
00:32:52,230 --> 00:32:53,490
We cultivators

445
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:55,490
are already going against heaven.

446
00:32:59,510 --> 00:33:00,620
Staying true to our hearts

447
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:03,050
is our only path.

448
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,380
Hu Jiaping

449
00:33:26,550 --> 00:33:27,660
must have noticed by now.

450
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:30,050
What do we do now?

451
00:33:32,550 --> 00:33:33,580
You're the old scumbag!

452
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:34,770
I'll slam you down!

453
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,340
I...

454
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:39,730
Stay true to our hearts

455
00:33:40,710 --> 00:33:42,100
and sneak into the Script Tower.

456
00:33:42,470 --> 00:33:43,970
You actually got the key.

457
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:46,250
Fine. I'll go in with you.

458
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:59,730
Legend says the Futu Tower in the academy

459
00:33:59,840 --> 00:34:02,010
holds many advanced cultivation techniques from across the realms.

460
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:04,380
There must be secret manuals on cultivating

461
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,860
spirit power and enhancing cultivation.

462
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:13,260
Brown is earth.

463
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:14,820
Red is fire.

464
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:16,420
Blue is water.

465
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:17,700
Green is wood.

466
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,380
Yellow is metal.

467
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:23,170
It's the Five Elements Formation.

468
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,130
- This... - Let's go.

469
00:34:50,720 --> 00:34:51,490
Already...?

470
00:35:25,030 --> 00:35:26,490
So many books.

471
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:32,940
How are we supposed to find it?

472
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:11,300
Let's do this.

473
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,170
I'll search this side.

474
00:36:13,630 --> 00:36:14,420
You search that side.

475
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:15,900
We'll each get what we need.

476
00:36:27,240 --> 00:36:30,090
I never expected so many fire-element texts.

477
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:50,490
Been searching for ages.

478
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:52,650
Nothing on cultivating spirit energy at all.

479
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,860
The Xuanhua Sacred Fire Record?

480
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:24,380
But Uncle said

481
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,650
this book has been lost for thousands of years.

482
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:39,650
Xuanhua Sacred Fire, Netherworld Dark Flame.

483
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:53,970
Among the 3,900 ways to control spirits in the world,

484
00:37:54,510 --> 00:37:56,130
the cultivation vessel is one of them.

485
00:37:56,740 --> 00:37:58,480
[The Record of Spirit Release]

486
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,130
Found it.

487
00:38:06,190 --> 00:38:07,050
I'll try this.

488
00:38:07,510 --> 00:38:08,220
See if it works.

489
00:38:12,150 --> 00:38:13,300
The Spirit-Releasing Immortal-Slaying Formation?

490
00:38:15,030 --> 00:38:16,300
Gather the spirit and condense it into the vessel.

491
00:38:17,110 --> 00:38:18,340
Nourish it with blood.

492
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:19,860
Channel it through the meridians.

493
00:38:20,670 --> 00:38:23,220
Release it all in one instant strike

494
00:38:25,550 --> 00:38:26,700
to take down the enemy with you.

495
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,650
This killing formation isn't about survival.

496
00:39:06,550 --> 00:39:08,010
It's a mutual destruction spell.

497
00:39:16,470 --> 00:39:18,090
Shanhua is barely hanging on.

498
00:39:18,190 --> 00:39:19,820
Don't delay any longer!

499
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:37,380
This is bad.

500
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:38,900
Did I practice it wrong?

501
00:39:49,470 --> 00:39:50,450
What are you trying to do?

502
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:51,780
Don't do anything reckless.

503
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:52,490
Don't speak.

504
00:40:02,360 --> 00:40:04,610
Calm your mind, regulate your breath, and clear your meridians.

505
00:40:05,550 --> 00:40:08,010
Observe outward form, discern inward heart.

506
00:40:11,510 --> 00:40:12,090
Thanks.

507
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:14,130
Focus.

508
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,380
I need to find Riyan

509
00:40:33,150 --> 00:40:33,900
before she notices.

510
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:05,880
[Zong Quan, Longming Sanctuary]

511
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,900
Divine Tree?

512
00:41:08,550 --> 00:41:10,720
[Cuixuan, Wuyue Court]

513
00:41:14,110 --> 00:41:15,530
Head to Chufeng Academy now.

514
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,940
Find out where the Divine Tree is.

515
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:18,860
[Qin Yangling, Wuyue Court]
Yes.

516
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:23,420
The aura of the Divine Tree!

517
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:42,840
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

518
00:41:43,160 --> 00:41:45,640
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

519
00:41:46,120 --> 00:41:49,440
